{"tid":2122486,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"63歲男染病亡 33人危殆創新高  專家：徵狀明顯先檢免延誤","createTime":"2020-07-24T04:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T08:18:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee5d429d2984a20241ae8fca2a4e57ad2516cd19","tid":2122486,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:30:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/ZVDDKGJML5WSCCP7GHENQQUKMA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FZVDDKGJML5WSCCP7GHENQQUKMA%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6HG9l5Y5fMjkJfB04Oq%2Bkmk%3D&h=381b4ae5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FZVDDKGJML5WSCCP7GHENQQUKMA%2F&h=ef925cc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/ZVDDKGJML5WSCCP7GHENQQUKMA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n63歲男染病亡 33人危殆創新高 <br />\n專家：徵狀明顯先檢免延誤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8_qZR5wlic-fp34or54mkS96sp4=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NDXPUL6L4DIWMMJ77K3NKBOE5M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8_qZR5wlic-fp34or54mkS96sp4%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNDXPUL6L4DIWMMJ77K3NKBOE5M.gif&h=fc9d9876&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本港再有一名居於慈雲山慈樂邨的63歲患者不敵武肺；圖為慈雲山中心何家達攝<br />\n<br />\n【武肺再爆發】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港武肺疫情嚴峻，醫管局公佈昨日再多一名病人死亡，令本港武肺死亡人數增至15人，現時仍有716名確診病人留醫，危殆人數創新高，增至33人。醫管局表示，危殆病人越來越多，與近日較多長者及長期病患者確診，部份人遲來醫院求診有關。有專家促請政府優先給予有明顯呼吸道病徵的高危人士進行檢測，讓他們可及早治療，以免令病情惡化。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局總行政經理庾慧玲昨於記者會上表示，。。。。。。。。。。。至今共有15名確診病人於公立醫院離世。<br />\n<br />\n她續稱，現時共有716名武肺確診病人分別於14間醫院留醫，其中33人情況危殆；14人情況嚴重，其餘669人情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n另再有35名確診病人出院，累計有1,379名確診或疑似病人康復出院。<br />\n<br />\n庚慧玲指出，危殆病人數目越來越多，。。。。。。。。。。。。呼籲無病徵市民到其他機構做測試。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n籲大眾勿湧公院做測試<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：觀塘帝盛變隔離中心 住客急退房<br />\n<br />\n對於本港武肺病人危殆人數創新高，。。。。。。。。。。。。情。」他又呼籲無病徵的市民不要湧醫院進行檢測，以騰出檢測空間予有病徵的人士，以免阻延他們治療。"},{"pid":"31c54186fd86a7e9810f01c41646f8513ab6032e","tid":2122486,"uid":155137,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:36:26.000Z","msg":"製造恐慌 <br />\n工照返 鐵照逼 五十年不變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5658bba97b450ac5cb068a8bb9a9d272ef6ada","tid":2122486,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:49:39.000Z","msg":"咁懷疑自己可能中咗，但又無病徵，又無咁多錢去私家做檢測，又唔畀/唔建議去公立睇。咁政府算唔算間接性叫人做流動隱形病人周圍傳播？<br />\n我唔可以唔返工㗎，有一家大細，手停口停。"},{"pid":"b49321ecce1e7340b30ea197af125dac006f3ae1","tid":2122486,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:41:05.000Z","msg":"林鄭考第一 香港1日驗6千一定係想煲大個疫情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978fbf91e1831dfecb959074d903879dc71ddd9e","tid":2122486,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8_qZR5wlic-fp34or54mkS96sp4=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NDXPUL6L4DIWMMJ77K3NKBOE5M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8_qZR5wlic-fp34or54mkS96sp4%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNDXPUL6L4DIWMMJ77K3NKBOE5M.gif&h=fc9d9876&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本港再有一名居於慈雲山慈樂邨的63歲患者不敵武肺；圖為慈雲山中心何家達攝<br />\n<br />\n張相影得唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60df61727f8d4c150b945342ac8001223dfa1eac","tid":2122486,"uid":28628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:17:56.000Z","msg":"On9 <br />\n根本呢d檢測量低到仆街<br />\n就叫人無病徵唔好驗<br />\n咁到時找唔到隱形病人<br />\n傳染俾其條人 咪一樣有問題<br />\n永遠做野都係治標唔治本<br />\n你加大檢測條數先啦<br />\n澳門都萬一個一日啦<br />